data.description: The best is yet to come in this centrally located sprawling ranch that sits on a lot and a half.   It is sure to be a favorite with room for everyone and offering plenty of privacy too.  On the main floor you will find large bedrooms and the work space in the kitchen is easy flow!  The in law apartement is attached by the utility room and can be opened for a family feel or closed for privacy.  The basement offers more living space and is plumbed for another full bath.  The bonus room has a large walk in closet for storage.   The large lot, fenced in yard, patio and pool make a perfecrt space to enertain!  Great house in a great location!
